WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.470
ALL CAPS reads as shouting — even if you only used it for

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:08.294
emphasis. Excessive exclamation points and question marks land the same way.

00:00:08.344 --> 00:00:12.814
Use punctuation and capitalization the same way you would in a professional letter.
